[SPEAKER_00] bo to kad krene velika devetnica

513
00:30:04,579 --> 00:30:05,500
[SPEAKER_00] u prvoj mjesecu

514
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] do 19.3.

515
00:30:06,599 --> 00:30:07,500
[SPEAKER_00] svi vole Josipa

516
00:30:07,500 --> 00:30:08,220
[SPEAKER_00] svaku srijedu

517
00:30:08,220 --> 00:30:09,079
[SPEAKER_00] na pun parking

518
00:30:09,079 --> 00:30:10,240
[SPEAKER_00] svi giju za Josipa

519
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:11,359
[SPEAKER_00] prođe devetnica

520
00:30:11,359 --> 00:30:12,160
[SPEAKER_00] više nikoga nema

521
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] dođe ljeto

522
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:14,140
[SPEAKER_00] niko mi ne zna za Josipa

523
00:30:14,140 --> 00:30:15,259
[SPEAKER_00] znači kad se odlučite

524
00:30:15,259 --> 00:30:16,059
[SPEAKER_00] za neki put

525
00:30:16,059 --> 00:30:16,859
[SPEAKER_00] za gospodina

526
00:30:16,859 --> 00:30:17,779
[SPEAKER_00] ili za nekog sveca

527
00:30:17,779 --> 00:30:18,740
[SPEAKER_00] onda morate tu biti

528
00:30:18,740 --> 00:30:19,980
[SPEAKER_00] 365 dana u godini

529
00:30:19,980 --> 00:30:20,660
[SPEAKER_00] i dan i noć

530
00:30:20,660 --> 00:30:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] znači ili ste s njim ili niste

531
00:30:22,500 --> 00:30:24,559
[SPEAKER_00] a sve drugo je površno

532
00:30:24,559 --> 00:30:25,640
[SPEAKER_00] i ono kad meni treba

533
00:30:25,640 --> 00:30:26,299
[SPEAKER_00] bože tu sam

534
00:30:26,299 --> 00:30:26,920
[SPEAKER_00] kad mi ne treba

535
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] kad mi je dobro

536
00:30:27,619 --> 00:30:30,140
[SPEAKER_00] bože sad nemam vremena za tebe

537
00:30:30,140 --> 00:30:31,180
[SPEAKER_00] to je naše ljudsko

538
00:30:31,180 --> 00:30:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] jednostavno to je tako

539
00:30:32,559 --> 00:30:34,079
[SPEAKER_00] i to se nikad neće skorijeniti

540
00:30:34,079 --> 00:30:35,160
[SPEAKER_00] ali eto

541
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost

542
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:39,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je ono što me dosta puta boli, kad ljudi ili kad neka, ne znam,

543
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:40,019
[SPEAKER_00] od 9.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3.00 u 3

544
00:30:40,019 --> 00:30:46,859
[SPEAKER_00] 9.30.00. Sad svi svetomanti ginu, hodočaste poste, post 13.6. više nema nikoga.

545
00:30:46,859 --> 00:30:52,299
[SPEAKER_00] Znači to je to naše ljudsko jednostavno ponašanje, ja bi reklam ne zahvalnu,

546
00:30:52,299 --> 00:30:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] jer ako nekoga voliš, ako si nekome vjeran, vjeran si mu i dobri u zlu i po danu i po noći

547
00:30:58,440 --> 00:31:01,299
[SPEAKER_00] i u sedmom mjesecu i dvanjesto mjesecu i trećem mjesecu.

548
00:31:01,299 --> 00:31:08,299
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mene je to moja vjera naučila i puno puta sam svoju obitelj zapostavila,

549
00:31:08,839 --> 00:31:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi je gospodin bio na prvom mjestu, ali on je to svaki put sve nagradio.

550
00:31:12,420 --> 00:31:18,539
[SPEAKER_00] Oni koji su mu vjerni nikad ne odstaje dužan, tako da je to.

551
00:31:18,539 --> 00:31:25,200
[SPEAKER_00] Što ne znači da trebate svoje obitelji zvog sve te mise ili hodočašća oštetiti,

552
00:31:25,200 --> 00:31:32,220
[SPEAKER_00] ali hoću reći, ne smijemo dopustiti danas naši svakidašnji poslovi,

553
00:31:32,220 --> 00:31:36,660
[SPEAKER_00] vežu da se nemićemo od posla ali od doma, da ne možemo nikoda ići,

554
00:31:36,660 --> 00:31:40,559
[SPEAKER_00] treba naći neku zdravu rametežu, da budemo aktivni u svojoj župi

555
00:31:40,559 --> 00:31:44,700
[SPEAKER_00] i da odrademo svoje poslo i u svojoj obitelji, obiteljski oblaze,

556
00:31:44,700 --> 00:31:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] a zato treba i puno moliti. Treba nam Duh Sveti da nas vodi,

557
00:31:48,460 --> 00:31:52,140
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi ljudi stvarno ne znamo sami, a Duh Sveti nema bolje poditelja od njega,

558
00:31:52,140 --> 00:31:55,779
[SPEAKER_00] vjerujte mi, taj upravlja samo tako.

559
00:31:57,240 --> 00:32:03,200
[SPEAKER_01] I danas je upravo vidio da sam upravo danas sebe pitala za ovo svjedočanstvo

560
00:32:03,200 --> 00:32:07,240
[SPEAKER_01] i ispalo je da je danas upravo objetnica i smrti tvoje majke

561
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:11,759
[SPEAKER_01] i jučer je bila ta šestest godišnjica zajednice.

562
00:32:11,759 --> 00:32:17,339
[SPEAKER_00] I Don Damiru je bio rođen, on je naš duhovnik,

563
00:32:17,339 --> 00:32:19,359
[SPEAKER_00] tako da baš je sve sastalo.

564
00:32:19,359 --> 00:32:22,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kažem, Josip baš zna, nekad nema ništa,

565
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:26,680
[SPEAKER_00] a nekad zna tako potrebite te neke događaja, situacije,

566
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:31,420
[SPEAKER_00] da tome da ostaneš šokiran i zapanjen, kako se to tako moglo spojiti.

567
00:32:31,420 --> 00:32:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu sam reći za kraj, u svakoj neboj vidite k Josipu,

568
00:32:36,019 --> 00:32:40,660
[SPEAKER_00] šta zgod muči, bolest, financije, zaposlenost, brak, djeca,

569
00:32:41,220 --> 00:32:44,140
[SPEAKER_00] sretna smrt, idete k Josipu, sve rješava.

570
00:32:44,140 --> 00:32:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, jedan svetac, univerzalan za sve i kogod puta želite,

571
00:32:48,039 --> 00:32:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] šutljiv, povučen, ne traži pažnju, pozornost,

572
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali tako moćan i jak.

573
00:32:53,380 --> 00:32:56,720
[SPEAKER_00] Ja kao počita neka sudjećanstva i u zadnjih godinu, dvije,

574
00:32:56,720 --> 00:33:03,440
[SPEAKER_00] ja se naježim od seline, ja ne mogu vjerovati

575
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] da tako nešto veliko se može dogoditi po jednoj običnoj devetnici

576
00:33:08,079 --> 00:33:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] ili molitvi, krunici, stvarno...

577
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:14,480
[SPEAKER_02] Da, u prvosti, mogu samo te kratko prekinuti.

578
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:18,819
[SPEAKER_02] Imamo par pitanja, ako možeš samo ponoviti ovu za pobožnost.

579
00:33:18,819 --> 00:33:22,720
[SPEAKER_02] To si mislila sad za pobožnost u prečestnom srcu Josipovi.

580
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,480
[SPEAKER_02] Da, je, mislila sam da to, da.

581
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:27,359
[SPEAKER_00] A sam malo u novitno što si mislila.

582
00:33:27,359 --> 00:33:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, to sam mislila, a samo mi u zajednici molimo pet prvih subota.

583
00:33:31,519 --> 00:33:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] Nismo pet dana za red, nego pet prvih subota molimo u zajednici

584
00:33:36,460 --> 00:33:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] i sljedeći se imamo četvrtu srijedu, pa završavamo u šestom mjesecu.

585
00:33:41,599 --> 00:33:44,160
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo je od devetnica koju mi sada molimo.

586
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:47,059
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da, prečestno srcu svetog Josipa, da, da.

587
00:33:47,059 --> 00:33:48,599
[SPEAKER_00] Da, stvarno je prekrasna.

588
00:33:48,599 --> 00:33:51,660
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam za to znala, to sam prije jednu godinu dana tako malo više saznala.

589
00:33:51,660 --> 00:33:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, baš mi je drago.

590
00:33:53,380 --> 00:33:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da je nekako tu osjećaj, nekako...

591
00:33:56,519 --> 00:33:59,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja molim 300 dnevna pobožnost, sve to mi je osjeća preko 10 godina.

592
00:33:59,940 --> 00:34:04,140
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam počela moliti u pobožnost, ja sam to samo tako čitala

593
00:34:04,140 --> 00:34:07,920
[SPEAKER_00] i bilo mi najvažnije onaj dio tamo za nakonu koju molim.

594
00:34:07,920 --> 00:34:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] Tu bi ja najviše pričala.

595
00:34:09,179 --> 00:34:11,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo drugo bi ja samo izpočitala.

596
00:34:11,079 --> 00:34:13,219
[SPEAKER_00] I onda sam s godinama kako sam molila,

597
00:34:13,219 --> 00:34:19,079
[SPEAKER_00] vidjela sam da vi znam napomet, ali počeli su mi sjedjet neke riječi.

598
00:34:19,079 --> 00:34:22,219
[SPEAKER_00] U toj pobožnosti gdje molimo tu neku svoju osobnu nakonu,

599
00:34:22,219 --> 00:34:25,719
[SPEAKER_00] tu se još molim za duše očistalištu i za umiruće.

600
00:34:26,239 --> 00:34:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam tek postala svjesna, puno kasnije,

601
00:34:29,519 --> 00:34:35,079
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo da kad se moliš Josipu da je on svetac za sretnu smrt

602
00:34:35,079 --> 00:34:38,559
[SPEAKER_00] i koliko je bitno moliti za duše očistalištu.

603
00:34:38,559 --> 00:34:41,500
[SPEAKER_00] To mi svi isto uzimamo zdravu za gotovo.

604
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] Sjetimo se za svi svete moliti, ne znam,

605
00:34:43,380 --> 00:34:45,639
[SPEAKER_00] Kruniću u devetcu dušama očistalištu,

606
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:47,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali mi smo svjesni, ne znam,

607
00:34:47,460 --> 00:34:49,619
[SPEAKER_00] meni je tu toliko osvijestila ta pobožnost,

608
00:34:49,619 --> 00:34:52,460
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je bitno je važno moliti za duše očistalištu,

609
00:34:52,460 --> 00:34:54,360
[SPEAKER_00] za naše pokojne i za sretnu smrt.

610
00:34:54,360 --> 00:34:56,559
[SPEAKER_00] Jer dok si je mladi, zdrav, ti misliš,

611
00:34:56,559 --> 00:34:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] ono, pred tobom je život, svijet je tvoj, ono,

612
00:34:58,559 --> 00:35:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] kao, neću nikad umriti.

613
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] A onda vrijeme prođe i prevarite,

614
00:35:02,500 --> 00:35:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] jer vrijeme još niko nije svladao,

615
00:35:04,619 --> 00:35:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] pa nećemo ni misliti ako živimo.

616
00:35:06,480 --> 00:35:08,099
[SPEAKER_00] Dođe tvoje vrijeme,

617
00:35:08,300 --> 00:35:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali nema liječe svjedočanstva od kad ti moliš cijelog svog života.

618
00:35:12,159 --> 00:35:14,760
[SPEAKER_00] Sveto mi je osvijest sretnu smrt,

619
00:35:14,760 --> 00:35:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] kad god ona bude, to je najviše što ti moliš učiniti.

620
00:35:17,300 --> 00:35:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam rekla, ono, sveti Josipe,

621
00:35:19,659 --> 00:35:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] ti me sam čekaj, pa mi idemo kad bude trebalo.

622
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:25,519
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, ništa.

623
00:35:25,519 --> 00:35:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala, prijeci Dajana, ili ima još kakvih pitanja.

624
00:35:28,260 --> 00:35:29,880
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sad baš malo čitam komentare,

625
00:35:29,880 --> 00:35:30,599
[SPEAKER_02] evo, stvarno,

626
00:35:30,599 --> 00:35:35,139
[SPEAKER_02] baš evo, prekrasno je svjedočanstvo

627
00:35:35,139 --> 00:35:37,639
[SPEAKER_02] i o sve što si rekla, baš je bilo nadatno to duhom svetljim.

628
00:35:37,639 --> 00:35:40,760
[SPEAKER_02] I ja mislim, imali smo još jedan upit

629
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:43,699
[SPEAKER_02] što se tiče rastomačenja

630
00:35:43,699 --> 00:35:45,719
[SPEAKER_02] prečisto srce Isusa,

631
00:35:45,719 --> 00:35:47,639
[SPEAKER_02] prečisto srce Josipovo,

632
00:35:47,639 --> 00:35:49,780
[SPEAKER_02] pa evo, samo ako možda Majo,

633
00:35:49,780 --> 00:35:52,039
[SPEAKER_02] želiš ti samo rastomačiti ili...

634
00:35:52,039 --> 00:35:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, hoću reći, primjer,

635
00:35:54,019 --> 00:35:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] moja zajednica je dio

636
00:35:55,380 --> 00:35:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] znači Salezijanske župe

637
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:58,940
[SPEAKER_00] koja je Marina župa

638
00:35:58,940 --> 00:36:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] i isto je dosta se njih čuđavalo

639
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:04,119
[SPEAKER_00] kao zašto ja toliko odižem Josipa

640
00:36:04,119 --> 00:36:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] a toliko Josipu pričam,

641
00:36:05,300 --> 00:36:06,340
[SPEAKER_00] kao da je Josip Bog,

642
00:36:06,340 --> 00:36:08,719
[SPEAKER_00] kao Marija iznad Josipa.

643
00:36:08,719 --> 00:36:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] Meni je to malo krivo pojmanje, ne znam.

644
00:36:11,940 --> 00:36:13,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam naučila od Malena

645
00:36:13,159 --> 00:36:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] da je Bog, Bog, Marija, Marija, Isus, Isus.

646
00:36:16,599 --> 00:36:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] I ja nikad nisam ješala

647
00:36:19,039 --> 00:36:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] niti pridavala nekome svecu

648
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] neku ulogu, neku

649
00:36:23,599 --> 00:36:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] moć koju ima.

650
00:36:25,900 --> 00:36:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] Zna se da je gospodinaš

651
00:36:27,579 --> 00:36:30,880
[SPEAKER_00] stvorite svega živog i neživog.

652
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da od njega sve dolazi drugo.

653
00:36:32,460 --> 00:36:34,519
[SPEAKER_00] I nekome njega su Isus i Marija

654
00:36:34,519 --> 00:36:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] i nekome njega dolaze sveci.

655
00:36:36,179 --> 00:36:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] Josip je prvi među svecima,

656
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:40,239
[SPEAKER_00] prvi do Marije Isusa.

657
00:36:40,820 --> 00:36:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] nije Josip taj koji vlada,

658
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:45,659
[SPEAKER_00] nekome konkurencija gospodinu Isusu.

659
00:36:45,659 --> 00:36:49,219
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, bilo je tako puno puta kao,

660
00:36:49,219 --> 00:36:51,780
[SPEAKER_00] evo sad recimo, taj hod je svake godine,

661
00:36:51,780 --> 00:36:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] Tunovski hod, pozdrav braći,

662
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,539
[SPEAKER_00] pradnjevcima, svetom duhu.

663
00:36:54,539 --> 00:36:57,340
[SPEAKER_00] Hod je svetog ante,

664
00:36:57,460 --> 00:36:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] 13. i 6.

665
00:36:58,219 --> 00:37:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] A mi ne znamo,

666
00:37:00,079 --> 00:37:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] hrvatski narod ne zna.

667
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:04,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, mi znamo za 19. i 3.

668
00:37:04,039 --> 00:37:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] kad slavimo svetog Josipa,

669
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:06,360
[SPEAKER_00] evo sad imamo u poneljak,

670
00:37:06,360 --> 00:37:08,139
[SPEAKER_00] prvi pet sveci Josip radnik,

671
00:37:08,139 --> 00:37:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je dosta više

672
00:37:09,380 --> 00:37:11,739
[SPEAKER_00] nekako obilježeno kao

673
00:37:11,739 --> 00:37:12,760
[SPEAKER_00] praznik rada,

674
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:15,360
[SPEAKER_00] a ne kao neki vjerski,

675
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] kao svetkovina svetog Josipa.

676
00:37:16,860 --> 00:37:17,840
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo 10. i 6.

677
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:19,739
[SPEAKER_00] Kad je hrvatski sabor

678
00:37:19,739 --> 00:37:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] izabrao svetog Josipa

679
00:37:20,860 --> 00:37:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] zaštitnika naša domovina Hrvatski.

680
00:37:23,019 --> 00:37:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi to ne znamo

681
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:26,960
[SPEAKER_00] i tu je konkurencija datuma.

682
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,420
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, 10. i 6. mi smo znali

683
00:37:28,420 --> 00:37:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] ići iz Zagreba

684
00:37:29,340 --> 00:37:31,739
[SPEAKER_00] na hodićaš svetom Josipu u Karlovac,

685
00:37:31,739 --> 00:37:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] a tad je hod svetom Anti.

686
00:37:33,079 --> 00:37:34,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ali sveci,

687
00:37:34,239 --> 00:37:34,780
[SPEAKER_00] to sam htjela reći,

688
00:37:34,780 --> 00:37:36,019
[SPEAKER_00] sveci nisu ljubomorni.

689
00:37:36,019 --> 00:37:38,320
[SPEAKER_00] I puno puta kad su mene ljudi pitali

690
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ti trokodižiš svetog Josipa,

691
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] pa nije on Bog,

692
00:37:40,739 --> 00:37:43,199
[SPEAKER_00] svaki put meni pokazalo

693
00:37:43,199 --> 00:37:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] da Marija zove Josipa,

694
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:45,820
[SPEAKER_00] da Marija voli

695
00:37:45,820 --> 00:37:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] da mi zovemo Josipa,

696
00:37:47,480 --> 00:37:48,860
[SPEAKER_00] da Marija nije ljubomorna

697
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:50,139
[SPEAKER_00] i da Marija sve zajedno

698
00:37:50,139 --> 00:37:51,699
[SPEAKER_00] s Josipom surađuje i radi.

699
00:37:51,699 --> 00:37:53,559
[SPEAKER_00] Pa moli ti, Marija ili Josipo,

700
00:37:53,559 --> 00:37:54,679
[SPEAKER_00] dođeš na ista vrata.

701
00:37:54,679 --> 00:37:56,199
[SPEAKER_00] Njih dvoje su uvijek zajedno

702
00:37:56,199 --> 00:37:57,760
[SPEAKER_00] i nikad nas neće ostaviti.

703
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:58,840
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se neće naljutiti,

704
00:37:58,840 --> 00:37:59,739
[SPEAKER_00] kom se god moli,

705
00:37:59,739 --> 00:38:01,559
[SPEAKER_00] ni sveti Ance se neće naljutiti.

706
00:38:01,559 --> 00:38:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

707
00:38:02,059 --> 00:38:04,059
[SPEAKER_00] to samo našim ljudskim glavama

708
00:38:04,059 --> 00:38:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] može postojati,

709
00:38:05,079 --> 00:38:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] jer mi tako ljudi gledamo među sobom.

710
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:07,260
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

711
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:10,739
[SPEAKER_00] sveci i Marija i Josip

712
00:38:10,739 --> 00:38:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] sve vole prihvaćaju

713
00:38:12,880 --> 00:38:13,739
[SPEAKER_00] i naljutiti se.

714
00:38:13,739 --> 00:38:15,679
[SPEAKER_00] Taka molitva srca

715
00:38:15,679 --> 00:38:16,420
[SPEAKER_00] gospodina.

716
00:38:16,420 --> 00:38:16,639
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

717
00:38:16,639 --> 00:38:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] I sve proizlazi od gospodina.

718
00:38:20,300 --> 00:38:20,739
[SPEAKER_00] Znači,

719
00:38:20,739 --> 00:38:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] onaj ko daje milosti,

720
00:38:21,880 --> 00:38:22,699
[SPEAKER_00] daje gospodin.

721
00:38:22,699 --> 00:38:24,239
[SPEAKER_00] Bio preko Isa,

722
00:38:24,239 --> 00:38:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] bilo preko Marije,

723
00:38:25,099 --> 00:38:26,019
[SPEAKER_00] bilo preko Josipa.

724
00:38:26,019 --> 00:38:26,780
[SPEAKER_00] Samo recimo,

725
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:27,820
[SPEAKER_00] Josip je moj put.

726
00:38:27,820 --> 00:38:29,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mene Josip doveo gospodinu,

727
00:38:29,599 --> 00:38:31,940
[SPEAKER_00] mene Josip otvorio

728
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:33,900
[SPEAKER_00] ta vrata vijera,

729
00:38:33,900 --> 00:38:34,860
[SPEAKER_00] da vidim dublje,

730
00:38:34,860 --> 00:38:36,360
[SPEAKER_00] da ne gledam površno.

731
00:38:36,579 --> 00:38:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam osjetila,

732
00:38:37,739 --> 00:38:38,820
[SPEAKER_00] deo mene je zabrao,

733
00:38:38,820 --> 00:38:40,199
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam ročno učio

734
00:38:40,199 --> 00:38:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] velike gospe,

735
00:38:41,139 --> 00:38:42,760
[SPEAKER_00] Marija me je donjela na svijet

736
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] i Josip me je izabrao

737
00:38:43,500 --> 00:38:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] za svog,

738
00:38:44,420 --> 00:38:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] kako kažem,

739
00:38:45,380 --> 00:38:45,960
[SPEAKER_00] učenika,

740
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:46,800
[SPEAKER_00] svog pojnika

741
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:48,719
[SPEAKER_00] i ja sam to tako prihvatila

742
00:38:48,719 --> 00:38:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] i tad najviše vidiš da

743
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] ne mora se događati

744
00:38:52,059 --> 00:38:53,639
[SPEAKER_00] ništa sad tu spektakularno,

745
00:38:53,639 --> 00:38:54,900
[SPEAKER_00] ali osjetiš u svom životu

746
00:38:54,900 --> 00:38:56,280
[SPEAKER_00] sa tim tvojim bitkama

747
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,320
[SPEAKER_00] ko tebe vodi,

748
00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:58,199
[SPEAKER_00] za koliko ti radiš

749
00:38:58,199 --> 00:38:59,019
[SPEAKER_00] i za koliko ti djeliš,

750
00:38:59,019 --> 00:38:59,780
[SPEAKER_00] koliko ti širiš,

751
00:38:59,780 --> 00:39:00,659
[SPEAKER_00] koliko ti voliš.

752
00:39:00,659 --> 00:39:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] Super.

753
00:39:02,219 --> 00:39:05,239
[SPEAKER_02] Puno ti hvala na svjedočanstvu

754
00:39:05,239 --> 00:39:08,260
[SPEAKER_02] i na ovim stvarno lijepim odaknutim riječima.

755
00:39:08,260 --> 00:39:09,920
[SPEAKER_02] Ja bih isto rekla samo,

756
00:39:09,920 --> 00:39:11,940
[SPEAKER_02] što se tiče naše vjere,

757
00:39:11,940 --> 00:39:13,239
[SPEAKER_02] sakramentalni život,

758
00:39:13,239 --> 00:39:14,260
[SPEAKER_02] sveta misa,

759
00:39:14,260 --> 00:39:15,760
[SPEAKER_02] redovita ispovijed,

760
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:17,380
[SPEAKER_02] ako možete otići

761
00:39:17,380 --> 00:39:17,960
[SPEAKER_02] i na hvaljnje

762
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:19,800
[SPEAKER_02] prezitom otrskom sakramentu.

763
00:39:19,800 --> 00:39:21,619
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da evo,

764
00:39:21,619 --> 00:39:22,920
[SPEAKER_02] to su nekakvi stupovi

765
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:25,440
[SPEAKER_02] kako bi zapravo svaki dan

766
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,599
[SPEAKER_02] imali dovoljno snage

767
00:39:26,599 --> 00:39:28,679
[SPEAKER_02] za sve ono što nam nosi svaki dan.

768
00:39:28,679 --> 00:39:30,039
[SPEAKER_02] Evo, Maio,

769
00:39:30,039 --> 00:39:31,300
[SPEAKER_02] imaš možda ti nešto za dodati?

770
00:39:31,300 --> 00:39:33,360
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim da smo sad već

771
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,380
[SPEAKER_02] dosta i produžili,

772
00:39:34,380 --> 00:39:36,599
[SPEAKER_02] pa da...

773
00:39:36,599 --> 00:39:37,320
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je, evo,

774
00:39:37,320 --> 00:39:38,219
[SPEAKER_01] bit ću kratka.

775
00:39:38,219 --> 00:39:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam prije svega

776
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:40,599
[SPEAKER_01] evo na strpljenju

777
00:39:40,599 --> 00:39:43,659
[SPEAKER_01] i da ste ostali s nama do kraja,

778
00:39:43,659 --> 00:39:44,679
[SPEAKER_01] da ste nas slušali.

779
00:39:44,820 --> 00:39:46,500
[SPEAKER_01] Bilja i Ruža nam je

780
00:39:46,500 --> 00:39:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] prekrasno svjedočanstvo dala.

781
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:50,599
[SPEAKER_01] Za vas koji ste zainteresirani

782
00:39:50,599 --> 00:39:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] i više saznato po božnosti,

783
00:39:52,139 --> 00:39:52,940
[SPEAKER_01] znači po božnost

784
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:54,420
[SPEAKER_01] pređe sam srcu Svetog Josipa

785
00:39:54,420 --> 00:39:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] je relativno nepozdata po božnost.

786
00:39:57,539 --> 00:39:59,420
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, nekako i naša želja

787
00:39:59,420 --> 00:40:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] na srcu je kroz ovu devetnicu

788
00:40:01,500 --> 00:40:04,320
[SPEAKER_01] proširit glas o toj po božnosti.

789
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:07,320
[SPEAKER_01] I voljeli bismo ikad bi

790
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:11,800
[SPEAKER_01] ako je bolja Božja

791
00:40:11,800 --> 00:40:13,380
[SPEAKER_01] da jednog dana se

792
00:40:13,380 --> 00:40:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] i ta srijeda

793
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:16,639
[SPEAKER_01] koja kada se slavi

794
00:40:16,639 --> 00:40:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] pređesto srce Svetog Josipa

795
00:40:18,079 --> 00:40:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] digne na razinu vlagdana

796
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,340
[SPEAKER_01] jer je

797
00:40:21,340 --> 00:40:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] pre sveto srce Isusovo

798
00:40:27,380 --> 00:40:28,940
[SPEAKER_01] je, znači, slavi se petak

799
00:40:28,940 --> 00:40:29,860
[SPEAKER_01] nakon tijelova.

800
00:40:29,860 --> 00:40:33,780
[SPEAKER_01] Subota, znači, odmah nakon tog petka

801
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:35,780
[SPEAKER_01] je bezgrišno srce Marino,

802
00:40:36,300 --> 00:40:39,820
[SPEAKER_01] a srijeda nakon te subote je dan

803
00:40:39,820 --> 00:40:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad se slavi pređesto srce Svetog Josipa

804
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,760
[SPEAKER_01] i evo, voljeli bismo

805
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:46,320
[SPEAKER_01] kad meni je nekako želja

806
00:40:46,320 --> 00:40:49,340
[SPEAKER_01] da to bude, ako je volja Božja,

807
00:40:49,340 --> 00:40:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] da bude to isto blagdan jednog dana.

808
00:40:52,619 --> 00:40:56,260
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da evo, za sve one koji žele saznat više

809
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:58,599
[SPEAKER_01] preporučamo s Pavlinski

810
00:40:58,599 --> 00:41:00,139
[SPEAKER_01] samostalno sveticama

811
00:41:00,139 --> 00:41:01,219
[SPEAKER_01] Kraj Karlovca

812
00:41:01,219 --> 00:41:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] čirit iso

813
00:41:03,059 --> 00:41:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] informaciju o toj pobožnosti

814
00:41:05,940 --> 00:41:07,159
[SPEAKER_01] tako da evo

815
00:41:07,159 --> 00:41:08,880
[SPEAKER_01] pozivamo vas da

816
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] da možda i tamo

817
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:15,300
[SPEAKER_01] da evo, da se obratite

818
00:41:15,300 --> 00:41:16,320
[SPEAKER_01] ako vas zanima više

819
00:41:16,320 --> 00:41:18,579
[SPEAKER_01] a s nama i dalje molite

820
00:41:18,579 --> 00:41:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] i ostanite u molitvi

821
00:41:20,940 --> 00:41:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] i evo svako vam dobro

822
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:23,699
[SPEAKER_01] i obilje Bože blagoslova

823
00:41:23,699 --> 00:41:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] i hvala na vremenu

824
00:41:24,960 --> 00:41:26,519
[SPEAKER_01] koje ste izvojili za ovu molitvu.

825
00:41:26,519 --> 00:41:27,699
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala svima.

826
00:41:27,699 --> 00:41:29,320
[SPEAKER_02] Želimo vas svima laku

827
00:41:29,320 --> 00:41:30,539
[SPEAKER_02] i glagoslođenu noć

828
00:41:30,539 --> 00:41:31,619
[SPEAKER_02] i vidimo se sutra

829
00:41:31,619 --> 00:41:32,760
[SPEAKER_02] u isto vrijeme

830
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:33,840
[SPEAKER_02] u 21 sat

831
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:34,719
[SPEAKER_02] na Kronici Hrvati

832
00:41:34,719 --> 00:41:35,519
[SPEAKER_02] svega svijeta.

833
00:41:35,519 --> 00:41:36,280
[SPEAKER_02] Pozdrav.

834
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:38,219
[SPEAKER_02] Pozdrav, Kuk.

835
00:41:54,960 --> 00:41:55,960
[UNKNOWN] Hvala svima.

